<doc>Host name of the appliance.</doc>
</param>
<param type="query" name="ip_addr">
<doc>The IPv6 or IPv4 address of the application interface. For example, 2002&#58;930&#58;a006&#58;164&#58;20c&#58;29ff&#58;fe41&#58;1c49 or 9.48.164.244.</doc>
</param>
<method name="GET" id="Find the next available HTTPS port for an interface"><doc>     To find the next available HTTPS port for a particular application interface,                       issue an HTTP GET command on the Reverse Proxy application interface resource URI.  </doc>
<request>
<doc>
 GET https://{appliance_hostname}/isam/wga_templates/httpsport?ip_addr={ip_addr}
 GET https://{appliance_hostname}/isam/wga_templates/httpsport?ip_addr=192.168.42.21
 </doc><param name="Authorization" style="header">
